NB.+ 1        1        1
NB.+1 0.778801 0.606531
NB.+1 0.606531 0.367879
NB.+1 0.472367  0.22313
NB. ---------------------------------------------------------
ft =: ([: % [: ^ ])~ ^"_ 0 ]
NB. ---------------------------------------------------------
Note 'build ft'
f =. [: % [: ^ ]
ft =. (f~(^"_ 0) ]) f.
)


